00:01:49.811 --> 00:01:57.619 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:57.652 --> 00:02:00.354 position:27% line:89% align:start
The bleeding won't stop.

00:02:00.387 --> 00:02:03.024 position:35% line:83% align:start
Yukimaru...
is he gonna die?

00:02:03.057 --> 00:02:04.892 position:10% line:83% align:start
Don't even think
stuff like that!

00:02:04.926 --> 00:02:06.360 position:5% line:89% align:start
No way is he gonna die!

00:02:06.393 --> 00:02:08.997 position:5% line:77% align:start
He won't, right?
Uh, yeah...

00:02:09.030 --> 00:02:15.069 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:15.103 --> 00:02:21.109 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:21.141 --> 00:02:24.311 position:24% line:83% align:start
We have to get the bullet
out right now!

00:02:24.344 --> 00:02:26.014 position:7% line:83% align:start
What is the nearest
port to us?

00:02:26.047 --> 00:02:27.447 position:21% line:89% align:start
That'd be Saint-Malo.

00:02:27.481 --> 00:02:30.585 position:5% line:83% align:start
But we'd be on the same route
the navy uses.

00:02:30.618 --> 00:02:32.887 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's a little far,
but Chaouen would allow us

00:02:32.920 --> 00:02:34.221 position:16% line:89% align:start
to travel on the surface.

00:02:34.254 --> 00:02:36.691 position:13% line:89% align:start
We do know a doctor there.

00:02:36.724 --> 00:02:38.191 position:41% line:83% align:start
Kaede!
Yes, sir!

00:02:38.225 --> 00:02:41.095 position:19% line:83% align:start
Go tell Makaba and Enju
to set course for Chaouen!

00:02:41.129 --> 00:02:42.797 position:21% line:89% align:start
Aye, aye!

00:02:42.830 --> 00:02:49.837 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:49.871 --> 00:02:51.539 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru...

00:02:51.572 --> 00:02:57.177 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:57.210 --> 00:03:03.017 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:03:03.051 --> 00:03:06.054 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Panting ]

00:03:06.087 --> 00:03:11.959 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:03:11.993 --> 00:03:17.899 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:03:17.932 --> 00:03:19.701 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:03:19.734 --> 00:03:23.137 position:5% line:83% align:start
Man: Kei's team didn't get there
in time?

00:03:23.171 --> 00:03:24.706 position:41% line:83% align:start
Man #2:
I heard they were wiped out.

00:03:24.739 --> 00:03:27.742 position:24% line:83% align:start
Man #3: Every last person
aboard the Hope...

00:03:27.775 --> 00:03:30.978 position:10% line:83% align:start
They say Yukimaru
was the only survivor.

00:03:31.012 --> 00:03:32.714 position:41% line:89% align:start
Even Lord Franz...

00:03:32.747 --> 00:03:39.352 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:03:39.386 --> 00:03:41.823 position:5% line:83% align:start
Doctor: There's nothing
you can do standing there.

00:03:41.856 --> 00:03:44.458 position:5% line:83% align:start
Go home.
Get some rest.

00:03:44.491 --> 00:03:52.567 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:03:52.600 --> 00:04:00.675 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:00.708 --> 00:04:08.750 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:08.783 --> 00:04:16.858 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:16.891 --> 00:04:25.032 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:31.939 --> 00:04:33.406 position:30% line:89% align:start
How he's doing?

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:35.543 position:52% line:83% align:start
How did you
prevent infection?

00:04:35.576 --> 00:04:37.310 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, uh...

00:04:37.344 --> 00:04:39.247 position:24% line:83% align:start
We used
some tobacco leaves.

00:04:39.279 --> 00:04:41.516 position:55% line:83% align:start
That was
a creative solution.

00:04:41.549 --> 00:04:44.451 position:13% line:83% align:start
If his injuries had festered,
he would have died.

00:04:44.484 --> 00:04:47.021 position:44% line:83% align:start
You may have just
saved his life.

00:04:47.054 --> 00:04:48.421 position:33% line:89% align:start
He's out of the woods.

00:04:48.455 --> 00:04:50.792 position:44% line:83% align:start
All he needs now
is a bit of time to rest

00:04:50.825 --> 00:04:53.426 position:27% line:89% align:start
and regain his strength.

00:04:53.460 --> 00:04:55.096 position:19% line:89% align:start
So then Yukimaru is --

00:04:55.129 --> 00:04:56.463 position:52% line:83% align:start
He'll make
a full recovery.

00:04:56.496 --> 00:04:58.599 position:7% line:89% align:start
Oh, thank goodness!

00:04:58.633 --> 00:05:01.334 position:5% line:83% align:start
Awesome!
That's our Yukimaru!

00:05:01.368 --> 00:05:03.771 position:5% line:83% align:start
What? You were the one who said
Yukimaru was gonna die!

00:05:03.805 --> 00:05:05.173 position:5% line:77% align:start
"Ye of little faith!"
No! You said that!

00:05:05.206 --> 00:05:06.574 position:24% line:83% align:start
Hey, knock it off,
you two!

00:05:06.607 --> 00:05:08.543 position:16% line:89% align:start
It was Fena.

00:05:08.576 --> 00:05:11.712 position:7% line:83% align:start
She was responsible
for saving Yukimaru's life.

00:05:11.746 --> 00:05:13.346 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Groans ]

00:05:13.380 --> 00:05:14.549 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're right.

00:05:14.582 --> 00:05:16.984 position:27% line:83% align:start
She stayed by him
and kept him safe.

00:05:17.018 --> 00:05:19.120 position:27% line:89% align:start
Like his guardian angel.

00:05:19.153 --> 00:05:21.889 position:47% line:89% align:start
[ Both grunt ]

00:05:21.923 --> 00:05:23.157 position:27% line:83% align:start
Both:
What a relief!

00:05:23.191 --> 00:05:24.892 position:5% line:89% align:start
Man, I was so worried!

00:05:24.926 --> 00:05:26.227 position:13% line:89% align:start
[ Both laugh ]

00:05:26.260 --> 00:05:28.963 position:33% line:89% align:start
I wouldn't be so sure.

00:05:28.996 --> 00:05:29.964 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Hmm?
-Hmm?

00:05:29.997 --> 00:05:31.933 position:33% line:89% align:start
You have it backwards.

00:05:31.966 --> 00:05:33.634 position:16% line:89% align:start
It was her...

00:05:33.668 --> 00:05:36.170 position:13% line:83% align:start
She forced him
into danger.

00:05:36.204 --> 00:05:37.672 position:33% line:89% align:start
How did she force him?

00:05:37.705 --> 00:05:39.941 position:10% line:83% align:start
There's no way you can blame
what happened on Fena.

00:05:39.974 --> 00:05:41.642 position:38% line:83% align:start
Yeah, they're right.
If those pirates hadn't tried --

00:05:41.676 --> 00:05:43.511 position:13% line:83% align:start
Shitan: Isn't the fact that
you're thinking that way

00:05:43.544 --> 00:05:47.414 position:19% line:83% align:start
just further proof that
you've fallen under her spell?

00:05:47.447 --> 00:05:49.517 position:27% line:83% align:start
Don't be fooled.
She's a witch.

00:05:49.550 --> 00:05:50.718 position:5% line:89% align:start
[ Jar clatters, water splashes ]

00:05:50.751 --> 00:05:52.286 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:05:52.320 --> 00:05:53.955 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ All gasp ]

00:05:53.988 --> 00:05:59.392 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:05:59.426 --> 00:06:01.996 position:19% line:83% align:start
What do you
mean by that?

00:06:02.029 --> 00:06:06.033 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm a...witch?

00:06:06.067 --> 00:06:07.635 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's nothing.

00:06:07.668 --> 00:06:09.270 position:58% line:89% align:start
Shitan.

00:06:09.303 --> 00:06:11.005 position:13% line:83% align:start
Please tell us
what you know.

00:06:11.038 --> 00:06:13.975 position:5% line:83% align:start
This seems like a secret
you shouldn't shoulder alone.

00:06:14.008 --> 00:06:21.015 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:06:21.048 --> 00:06:24.018 position:5% line:83% align:start
With Franz's untimely death,
the only clues left

00:06:24.051 --> 00:06:28.556 position:7% line:83% align:start
to help us find it
lie within Fena's memories.

00:06:28.589 --> 00:06:32.260 position:7% line:83% align:start
But she comes from
a long line of witches.

00:06:32.293 --> 00:06:33.694 position:55% line:89% align:start
Witches?

00:06:33.728 --> 00:06:37.598 position:5% line:83% align:start
Those who corrupt men
and bring about their downfall.

00:06:37.632 --> 00:06:39.567 position:19% line:83% align:start
It was true
of her mother.

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:43.137 position:5% line:83% align:start
I know of a man who was
driven mad by her charms.

00:06:43.170 --> 00:06:45.573 position:33% line:83% align:start
What are you asking me
to do then?

00:06:45.606 --> 00:06:48.009 position:19% line:83% align:start
Keep watch
over Yukimaru.

00:06:48.042 --> 00:06:52.479 position:5% line:83% align:start
If he should ever appear to have
fallen under her spell...

00:06:52.513 --> 00:06:54.447 position:5% line:83% align:start
you must kill.
[ Gasps ]

00:06:57.952 --> 00:07:02.123 position:10% line:83% align:start
Even if you gave me the order,
Master,

00:07:02.156 --> 00:07:04.992 position:50% line:83% align:start
I could never
kill Yukimaru.

00:07:05.026 --> 00:07:06.761 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'm aware of that.

00:07:06.794 --> 00:07:09.363 position:5% line:83% align:start
But the one you must
strike down...

00:07:09.397 --> 00:07:12.333 position:10% line:89% align:start
is not Yukimaru.

00:07:12.366 --> 00:07:15.937 position:10% line:89% align:start
It is the witch.

00:07:15.970 --> 00:07:18.205 position:27% line:89% align:start
Is that really...

00:07:18.239 --> 00:07:20.007 position:21% line:89% align:start
what you think of me?

00:07:23.344 --> 00:07:24.745 position:41% line:89% align:start
Shitan.

00:07:24.779 --> 00:07:27.315 position:44% line:77% align:start
Shitan, I'm not --
It's the truth.

00:07:27.348 --> 00:07:30.084 position:21% line:83% align:start
The others chose you
over the island.

00:07:30.117 --> 00:07:31.419 position:27% line:83% align:start
Wait,
that's not fair.

00:07:31.484 --> 00:07:33.254 position:38% line:77% align:start
She didn't force us.
And now...

00:07:33.287 --> 00:07:35.455 position:21% line:83% align:start
we're all hunted men
because of you.

00:07:35.488 --> 00:07:36.791 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:07:36.824 --> 00:07:39.360 position:21% line:83% align:start
We spent years laying
a foundation

00:07:39.393 --> 00:07:41.095 position:24% line:83% align:start
and building trust
in one another!

00:07:41.128 --> 00:07:42.863 position:24% line:89% align:start
Risking our lives!

00:07:42.897 --> 00:07:45.433 position:38% line:83% align:start
But then
in just a few short weeks,

00:07:45.465 --> 00:07:48.235 position:21% line:77% align:start
you come along and --
Shitan!

00:07:48.269 --> 00:07:50.705 position:44% line:83% align:start
What the heck has
gotten into you?

00:07:50.738 --> 00:07:53.507 position:19% line:83% align:start
Every single action we made
was a conscious choice.

00:07:53.541 --> 00:07:54.809 position:47% line:89% align:start
Not some spell.

00:07:54.842 --> 00:07:57.178 position:41% line:83% align:start
So don't blame this
on her!

00:07:57.211 --> 00:08:00.581 position:19% line:77% align:start
I'm blaming her, am I?
Yeah!

00:08:00.614 --> 00:08:02.049 position:41% line:83% align:start
All you're doing is
displacing your anger

00:08:02.083 --> 00:08:04.585 position:27% line:89% align:start
and lashing out at Fena!

00:08:04.618 --> 00:08:05.920 position:33% line:89% align:start
Look, Shitan.

00:08:05.953 --> 00:08:07.922 position:33% line:83% align:start
If you really
think about it --

00:08:07.955 --> 00:08:10.558 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:08:12.226 --> 00:08:15.229 position:50% line:83% align:start
10 years ago
and now once again...

00:08:15.262 --> 00:08:18.032 position:44% line:89% align:start
he's been hurt...

00:08:18.065 --> 00:08:19.734 position:47% line:89% align:start
because of you.

00:08:19.767 --> 00:08:25.906 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:08:25.940 --> 00:08:32.146 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:08:33.647 --> 00:08:36.884 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Seagulls calling ]

00:08:40.788 --> 00:08:43.124 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:08:43.157 --> 00:08:45.960 position:10% line:89% align:start
[ Wood clacks, body thumps ]

00:08:45.993 --> 00:08:49.363 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh, wow!
You won!

00:08:49.397 --> 00:08:51.032 position:13% line:83% align:start
You won again,
Yukimaru!

00:08:51.065 --> 00:08:53.601 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're awesome!

00:08:53.634 --> 00:08:55.770 position:55% line:83% align:start
Yukimaru.
Yes?

00:08:55.803 --> 00:08:58.572 position:52% line:83% align:start
That strike
was well executed.

00:08:58.606 --> 00:09:00.574 position:38% line:83% align:start
Thank you very much.

00:09:00.608 --> 00:09:02.810 position:10% line:83% align:start
But the swordsmen
on the battlefield

00:09:02.843 --> 00:09:04.745 position:21% line:83% align:start
won't be
as weak as this one.

00:09:04.779 --> 00:09:07.481 position:13% line:83% align:start
Be sure to take
that lesson to heart.

00:09:07.516 --> 00:09:09.884 position:78% line:83% align:start
Right.
You may go rest.

00:09:09.917 --> 00:09:14.955 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:09:14.989 --> 00:09:19.994 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:09:20.027 --> 00:09:21.462 position:33% line:89% align:start
How pathetic.

00:09:21.495 --> 00:09:26.267 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:09:38.145 --> 00:09:40.714 position:58% line:83% align:start
Makaba:
No, not those.

00:09:40.748 --> 00:09:41.615 position:27% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:09:41.649 --> 00:09:43.350 position:52% line:83% align:start
Those ones
are the rejects.

00:09:43.384 --> 00:09:44.952 position:10% line:89% align:start
They're so stiff,

00:09:44.985 --> 00:09:48.489 position:5% line:83% align:start
so it's impossible to control
the direction the arrow will go.

00:09:48.523 --> 00:09:49.790 position:64% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:09:49.824 --> 00:09:53.327 position:24% line:83% align:start
So these are the rejects,
then?

00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:56.497 position:50% line:89% align:start
Just like me.

00:09:56.531 --> 00:09:59.500 position:33% line:83% align:start
Makaba, would you mind
if I tried one out?

00:09:59.534 --> 00:10:04.004 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:04.038 --> 00:10:05.873 position:38% line:77% align:start
[ Sighs ]
[ Footsteps approach ]

00:10:05.906 --> 00:10:07.975 position:64% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:10:08.008 --> 00:10:15.282 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:15.316 --> 00:10:18.986 position:16% line:83% align:start
How is it --
Makaba's long bow?

00:10:19.019 --> 00:10:20.254 position:58% line:89% align:start
Tricky.

00:10:20.287 --> 00:10:22.857 position:38% line:83% align:start
They fly a bit wide.
Huh?

00:10:22.890 --> 00:10:24.925 position:52% line:83% align:start
The arrows
don't listen to me.

00:10:24.959 --> 00:10:26.694 position:50% line:83% align:start
They won't go
where I aim them.

00:10:26.727 --> 00:10:29.964 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, then,
why don't you listen to them?

00:10:29.997 --> 00:10:31.165 position:61% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:31.198 --> 00:10:35.669 position:5% line:83% align:start
Why not aim your shot
where the arrow wants to go?

00:10:35.703 --> 00:10:37.371 position:16% line:89% align:start
Listen to it.

00:10:37.404 --> 00:10:44.546 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:44.579 --> 00:10:47.681 position:41% line:83% align:start
Aim where the arrow
wants to go.

00:10:47.715 --> 00:10:50.918 position:38% line:83% align:start
Don't let the target
lead you astray.

00:10:50.951 --> 00:10:56.390 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:56.423 --> 00:10:58.392 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, wow.

00:10:58.425 --> 00:11:01.462 position:55% line:89% align:start
I hit it!

00:11:01.495 --> 00:11:03.864 position:7% line:83% align:start
You're pretty good
at that.

00:11:03.898 --> 00:11:07.134 position:33% line:83% align:start
I haven't mastered it,
but I will.

00:11:07.168 --> 00:11:13.841 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:11:16.611 --> 00:11:18.779 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Panting ]

00:11:21.882 --> 00:11:25.119 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:11:25.152 --> 00:11:27.354 position:33% line:89% align:start
What, Brule?

00:11:27.388 --> 00:11:29.156 position:5% line:89% align:start
Fena: Good job, Brule!

00:11:29.190 --> 00:11:31.859 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ Panting ]

00:11:37.464 --> 00:11:40.134 position:38% line:89% align:start
I finally found you!

00:11:40.167 --> 00:11:41.869 position:44% line:89% align:start
Fena?

00:11:45.239 --> 00:11:47.208 position:5% line:83% align:start
Shitan, I --
Go away.

00:11:48.909 --> 00:11:50.711 position:7% line:83% align:start
Listen, the others
filled me in on --

00:11:50.744 --> 00:11:54.215 position:41% line:89% align:start
Didn't you hear me?

00:11:54.248 --> 00:11:56.585 position:55% line:89% align:start
Go away.

00:11:56.618 --> 00:11:58.687 position:44% line:83% align:start
If they told you,
you should know

00:11:58.752 --> 00:12:00.287 position:55% line:83% align:start
my orders
are to kill you.

00:12:00.321 --> 00:12:01.623 position:16% line:89% align:start
But Shitan...

00:12:01.656 --> 00:12:04.626 position:5% line:89% align:start
You would never do that.

00:12:04.659 --> 00:12:06.493 position:50% line:89% align:start
You wouldn't.

00:12:06.528 --> 00:12:08.963 position:38% line:83% align:start
'Cause you taught me
how to use a bow.

00:12:08.996 --> 00:12:11.633 position:35% line:83% align:start
I know very well that
I'm an awful student.

00:12:11.666 --> 00:12:14.703 position:33% line:83% align:start
But you took your time
to teach me.

00:12:14.735 --> 00:12:16.370 position:13% line:89% align:start
And besides...

00:12:16.403 --> 00:12:19.473 position:5% line:83% align:start
I still can't even hit
the broad side of a barn!

00:12:19.507 --> 00:12:21.041 position:44% line:77% align:start
Huh?
Oh, you heard me!

00:12:21.075 --> 00:12:22.677 position:55% line:83% align:start
I'm still
terrible at this!

00:12:22.711 --> 00:12:24.211 position:27% line:83% align:start
Which means if you don't
keep teaching me,

00:12:24.245 --> 00:12:25.813 position:50% line:83% align:start
I don't think
I'll ever hit anything!

00:12:25.846 --> 00:12:27.649 position:16% line:77% align:start
Now, wait just a minute --
Is that what you want?

00:12:27.682 --> 00:12:29.316 position:41% line:83% align:start
If your student is
that incompetent,

00:12:29.350 --> 00:12:30.851 position:24% line:83% align:start
then it will just reflect
badly on you!

00:12:30.884 --> 00:12:32.353 position:33% line:83% align:start
What are you
babbling about?

00:12:32.386 --> 00:12:33.688 position:35% line:89% align:start
What I'm saying is...

00:12:33.722 --> 00:12:36.691 position:44% line:83% align:start
is I want to keep
traveling with you.

00:12:36.725 --> 00:12:38.526 position:44% line:89% align:start
You and Yukimaru!

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:40.662 position:38% line:89% align:start
Karin and the twins!

00:12:40.695 --> 00:12:42.329 position:41% line:89% align:start
Tsubaki and Makaba.

00:12:42.363 --> 00:12:44.164 position:44% line:89% align:start
With all of you.

00:12:44.198 --> 00:12:45.600 position:41% line:89% align:start
For the rest of...

00:12:45.634 --> 00:12:48.068 position:55% line:89% align:start
my life.

00:12:48.102 --> 00:12:50.237 position:75% line:83% align:start
Fena...
And furthermore!

00:12:50.271 --> 00:12:52.741 position:7% line:83% align:start
If I were a witch,
don't you think I'd use my magic

00:12:52.773 --> 00:12:55.109 position:13% line:83% align:start
to make myself
a better archer?

00:12:55.142 --> 00:12:56.443 position:61% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:12:56.477 --> 00:12:58.846 position:5% line:83% align:start
I don't fly on a broomstick
or cackle or have a black cat!

00:12:58.879 --> 00:13:01.015 position:10% line:83% align:start
Though I do have
a big white dog!

00:13:01.048 --> 00:13:02.751 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm always getting
smacked on the head!

00:13:02.783 --> 00:13:04.686 position:7% line:83% align:start
That or I'm getting
tossed in the ocean!

00:13:04.719 --> 00:13:06.253 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm dumb!
Not a morning person!

00:13:06.287 --> 00:13:07.421 position:5% line:89% align:start
Not remotely in shape!

00:13:07.454 --> 00:13:09.323 position:5% line:83% align:start
I can't use a single weapon
or a crystal ball!

00:13:09.356 --> 00:13:10.759 position:5% line:89% align:start
I can't predict the future!

00:13:10.791 --> 00:13:12.493 position:5% line:83% align:start
You could search the whole world
from top to bottom

00:13:12.527 --> 00:13:14.962 position:16% line:83% align:start
and not find
a single witch like...

00:13:14.995 --> 00:13:16.698 position:30% line:89% align:start
me?

00:13:16.731 --> 00:13:17.766 position:24% line:89% align:start
Shitan?

00:13:17.798 --> 00:13:21.402 position:21% line:89% align:start
Shitan?

00:13:21.435 --> 00:13:23.605 position:7% line:89% align:start
What are you doing?

00:13:23.638 --> 00:13:26.675 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:13:26.708 --> 00:13:30.411 position:50% line:89% align:start
[ Laughing ]

00:13:30.444 --> 00:13:33.180 position:52% line:77% align:start
Are you...
alright?

00:13:34.214 --> 00:13:37.652 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Sighs ]

00:13:37.686 --> 00:13:39.953 position:13% line:83% align:start
You were always whacking her,
Yukimaru.

00:13:39.987 --> 00:13:42.356 position:58% line:83% align:start
And now
I think I know why.

00:13:42.389 --> 00:13:45.392 position:64% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:13:45.426 --> 00:13:47.227 position:5% line:83% align:start
Alright.
Let's get a move on.

00:13:47.261 --> 00:13:49.798 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:13:49.830 --> 00:13:50.831 position:24% line:89% align:start
Shitan?

00:13:50.864 --> 00:13:53.100 position:44% line:89% align:start
Let's head back.

00:13:53.133 --> 00:13:56.136 position:19% line:83% align:start
We'll set out again as soon
as Yukimaru wakes up.

00:13:58.472 --> 00:14:00.107 position:35% line:89% align:start
Well, are you coming?

00:14:00.140 --> 00:14:10.084 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:14:21.295 --> 00:14:23.598 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Groans ]

00:14:31.573 --> 00:14:32.906 position:35% line:89% align:start
I can't...

00:14:32.940 --> 00:14:36.511 position:33% line:89% align:start
feel my legs.

00:14:36.544 --> 00:14:38.212 position:44% line:89% align:start
Fena!

00:14:38.245 --> 00:14:41.014 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Groans ]

00:14:47.722 --> 00:14:50.658 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ Brule groans ]

00:14:59.032 --> 00:15:00.802 position:52% line:83% align:start
Yukimaru: Fena.
[ Groans ]

00:15:00.835 --> 00:15:02.403 position:64% line:89% align:start
Fena.

00:15:02.436 --> 00:15:04.739 position:61% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:15:04.773 --> 00:15:06.473 position:61% line:89% align:start
Fena.

00:15:06.508 --> 00:15:08.676 position:61% line:89% align:start
Fena!

00:15:08.710 --> 00:15:16.684 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:15:16.718 --> 00:15:18.586 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Smack! ]

00:15:18.620 --> 00:15:21.689 position:10% line:83% align:start
Ow!
[ Brule howls ]

00:15:21.723 --> 00:15:26.528 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Groaning ]

00:15:26.561 --> 00:15:28.462 position:21% line:83% align:start
Was that
really necessary?!

00:15:28.495 --> 00:15:31.432 position:16% line:83% align:start
I thought I had lost my legs
for a second.

00:15:31.465 --> 00:15:32.567 position:50% line:89% align:start
I was scared.

00:15:32.600 --> 00:15:35.035 position:19% line:89% align:start
Oh, sorry.

00:15:35.068 --> 00:15:39.072 position:52% line:83% align:start
Has Shitan
come around yet?

00:15:41.975 --> 00:15:43.912 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm not sure.

00:15:43.944 --> 00:15:46.380 position:10% line:89% align:start
But I am hopeful.

00:15:46.413 --> 00:15:48.716 position:58% line:83% align:start
So then
where was he yesterday?

00:15:48.750 --> 00:15:51.051 position:5% line:83% align:start
Well, the others went back
to the ship,

00:15:51.084 --> 00:15:52.453 position:5% line:89% align:start
but Shitan and the doctor

00:15:52.486 --> 00:15:54.087 position:19% line:83% align:start
went out to
the entertainment district.

00:15:54.121 --> 00:15:55.456 position:5% line:83% align:start
He said he knew a bar
with pretty --

00:15:55.489 --> 00:15:57.692 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yeah, he's fine, then.

00:15:57.725 --> 00:15:59.460 position:19% line:89% align:start
You think?

00:15:59.493 --> 00:16:01.195 position:27% line:89% align:start
You don't need to worry.

00:16:03.598 --> 00:16:06.266 position:50% line:89% align:start
But still...

00:16:06.300 --> 00:16:08.736 position:50% line:83% align:start
Why were you
on that navy ship?

00:16:08.770 --> 00:16:13.207 position:10% line:83% align:start
Oh. Well. that's
a...long story.

00:16:13.240 --> 00:16:15.610 position:52% line:83% align:start
I'd like to
hear about it.

00:16:15.643 --> 00:16:17.277 position:52% line:89% align:start
If you can.

00:16:17.311 --> 00:16:24.853 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:16:24.886 --> 00:16:32.627 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:16:32.660 --> 00:16:40.400 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:16:40.434 --> 00:16:47.976 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:16:48.008 --> 00:16:50.344 position:24% line:89% align:start
I see.

00:16:50.377 --> 00:16:52.747 position:5% line:83% align:start
My world's been turned
upside down.

00:16:52.780 --> 00:16:56.784 position:7% line:83% align:start
I haven't been able
to process it.

00:16:56.818 --> 00:16:59.721 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm so sorry.

00:16:59.754 --> 00:17:01.589 position:44% line:89% align:start
Why're you sorry?

00:17:01.623 --> 00:17:05.994 position:5% line:83% align:start
Before...I acted all upbeat
and carefree with Shitan.

00:17:06.026 --> 00:17:09.597 position:16% line:83% align:start
But all that
was only just an act.

00:17:09.631 --> 00:17:13.635 position:5% line:83% align:start
I started out thinking
I was just Fena Houtman.

00:17:13.668 --> 00:17:16.938 position:35% line:83% align:start
Then I somehow became
Fena of Shangri-La.

00:17:16.971 --> 00:17:20.008 position:27% line:83% align:start
After that, I was called
the White Marginal.

00:17:20.040 --> 00:17:21.943 position:30% line:83% align:start
And now suddenly people
are calling me

00:17:21.976 --> 00:17:25.078 position:33% line:89% align:start
"Princess" or "witch."

00:17:25.112 --> 00:17:27.015 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm left wondering...

00:17:27.047 --> 00:17:28.750 position:44% line:89% align:start
who am I, really?

00:17:30.952 --> 00:17:32.252 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's possible...

00:17:32.286 --> 00:17:34.556 position:10% line:83% align:start
you'll only find
your answers there.

00:17:36.524 --> 00:17:40.762 position:5% line:83% align:start
The place I promised Franz
I'd take you to.

00:17:40.795 --> 00:17:42.496 position:27% line:89% align:start
Eden.

00:17:46.300 --> 00:17:48.435 position:41% line:89% align:start
I want to go there.

00:17:48.468 --> 00:17:50.638 position:35% line:83% align:start
But at the same time,
I don't.

00:17:52.874 --> 00:17:55.375 position:10% line:89% align:start
I had a thought.

00:17:55.409 --> 00:17:57.845 position:5% line:83% align:start
Maybe I could keep on
traveling with you guys

00:17:57.879 --> 00:18:00.380 position:5% line:89% align:start
for the rest of my life.

00:18:00.414 --> 00:18:02.850 position:16% line:83% align:start
Going around
to various islands

00:18:02.884 --> 00:18:05.485 position:16% line:83% align:start
and visiting
unknown places.

00:18:05.520 --> 00:18:07.722 position:10% line:83% align:start
We could have fun
every day.

00:18:09.857 --> 00:18:11.258 position:10% line:89% align:start
If I did that...

00:18:11.291 --> 00:18:14.629 position:16% line:83% align:start
I could stay
who I am right now.

00:18:14.662 --> 00:18:19.166 position:7% line:83% align:start
And then, that way,
nothing would have to change.

00:18:19.199 --> 00:18:20.902 position:52% line:83% align:start
That's what
you're afraid of?

00:18:20.935 --> 00:18:23.705 position:47% line:89% align:start
Moving forward?

00:18:23.738 --> 00:18:27.041 position:7% line:89% align:start
I guess I might be.

00:18:27.075 --> 00:18:28.208 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:18:28.241 --> 00:18:29.644 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm not helpful.

00:18:29.677 --> 00:18:32.412 position:44% line:89% align:start
Don't apologize.

00:18:32.446 --> 00:18:35.315 position:27% line:83% align:start
Wherever you want to go,
I'll go with you.

00:18:35.349 --> 00:18:39.186 position:41% line:83% align:start
Wherever you stop,
I'll stop too.

00:18:39.219 --> 00:18:43.992 position:13% line:89% align:start
Like the birds on the island.

00:18:44.025 --> 00:18:45.392 position:38% line:89% align:start
When I was little...

00:18:45.425 --> 00:18:49.664 position:44% line:83% align:start
my father told me
a great man once said,

00:18:49.697 --> 00:18:51.264 position:5% line:89% align:start
"In this fleeting life,

00:18:51.298 --> 00:18:54.201 position:5% line:83% align:start
there are two moments of joy
above all others.

00:18:54.234 --> 00:18:57.905 position:5% line:83% align:start
When we are born into this world
and take our first breath.

00:18:57.939 --> 00:19:02.510 position:5% line:83% align:start
And when we learn what we were
put on this earth to do."

00:19:05.613 --> 00:19:08.315 position:10% line:83% align:start
I don't know what
you'll find there.

00:19:08.348 --> 00:19:12.954 position:5% line:83% align:start
But I think the answers you seek
will be in Eden.

00:19:12.987 --> 00:19:15.857 position:10% line:83% align:start
To questions like
who you are.

00:19:15.890 --> 00:19:20.327 position:24% line:83% align:start
Also...
as to why you and I met.

00:19:23.097 --> 00:19:24.799 position:35% line:89% align:start
I will keep you safe.

00:19:24.832 --> 00:19:27.669 position:35% line:89% align:start
Until my last breath.

00:19:27.702 --> 00:19:29.737 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru...

00:19:29.771 --> 00:19:33.141 position:7% line:83% align:start
To make sure that you are never
put in danger again...

00:19:33.173 --> 00:19:36.811 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'll strive to become
even stronger.

00:19:36.844 --> 00:19:39.881 position:61% line:89% align:start
Fena.

00:19:39.914 --> 00:19:42.016 position:41% line:89% align:start
Let's go together.

00:19:42.050 --> 00:19:44.152 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ Groans ]

00:19:44.184 --> 00:19:45.920 position:55% line:83% align:start
Yukimaru!
Are you okay?

00:19:45.953 --> 00:19:47.555 position:38% line:89% align:start
Does something hurt?

00:19:47.588 --> 00:19:50.490 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:50.525 --> 00:19:53.127 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:19:53.161 --> 00:19:58.099 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:58.132 --> 00:19:59.767 position:52% line:89% align:start
Y-Yukimaru?

00:19:59.801 --> 00:20:01.002 position:41% line:89% align:start
What's the matter?

00:20:01.035 --> 00:20:02.570 position:27% line:89% align:start
Fena.

00:20:02.603 --> 00:20:03.838 position:61% line:89% align:start
Yes?

00:20:03.871 --> 00:20:05.372 position:7% line:89% align:start
Whatever happens...

00:20:05.405 --> 00:20:07.942 position:24% line:83% align:start
I swear
to always protect you.

00:20:12.613 --> 00:20:14.849 position:19% line:89% align:start
My hand...

00:20:14.882 --> 00:20:18.186 position:7% line:89% align:start
will never again...

00:20:18.218 --> 00:20:19.854 position:10% line:89% align:start
let go of yours.

00:20:19.887 --> 00:20:28.096 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

